## for qemu guest (fedora 25g, arch host)
sudo dnf install xorg-x11-drv-qxl
sudo dnf install spice-vdagent
- display settings:
    - Type: Spice server
    - Listen Type: address
    - Address: listen type
    - openGL NOT checked
- video settings:
    - Model: QXL

## caps-esc mapping
- xmodmap doesn't seem to work
- install/use gnome-tweak-tool
